    public abstract class NodeBox
extends javafx.scene.layout.BorderPane
implements NodeBoxObserver, Algorithm
    NodeBox class. The main definition of what is an 'Node' is here.
    Version:
    v1.0
    Author:
    Daniel, Davidson.
    API Note:
    All filters/nodes should extend NodeBox class.
